quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  7,109,"Àwọn ìjòyè nínú ìjọ Fir‘aon wí pé: \"Dájúdájú èyí ni onímọ̀ nípa idán pípa"
  7,110,"Ó fẹ́ ko yín kúrò lórí ilẹ̀ yín ni.\" (Fir‘aon wí pé: ) “Kí ni ohun tí ẹ máa mú wá ní ìmọ̀ràn?”"
  7,111,"Wọ́n sì wí pé: \"Dá òun àti arákùnrin rẹ̀ dúró ná, kí o sì rán àwọn akónijọ sí àwọn ìlú"
  7,112,(pé) kí gbogbo onímọ̀ nípa idán pípa wá bá ọ
  7,113,"Àwọn òpìdán sì dé wá bá Fir‘aon. Wọ́n wí pé: “Dájúdájú ẹ̀san gbọ́dọ̀ wà fún wa tí àwa bá jẹ́ olùborí.”"
  7,114,"Ó wí pé: “Bẹ́ẹ̀ ni. Àti pé dájúdájú ẹ̀yin gbọ́dọ̀ wà nínú àwọn alásùn-únmọ́ (mi).”"
  7,115,"(Àwọn òpìdán) wí pé: “Mūsā, o máa (kọ́kọ́) ju ọ̀pá sílẹ̀ ni, tàbí àwa ni a máa (kọ́kọ́) jù ú sílẹ̀.”"
  7,116,"(Ànábì Mūsā) sọ pé: “Ẹ ju (tiyín) sílẹ̀ (ná).” Nígbà tí wọ́n jù ú sílẹ̀, wọ́n fi pidán lójú àwọn ènìyàn. Wọ́n sì ṣẹ̀rùbà wọ́n. Wọ́n wá pẹ̀lú idán ńlá"
  7,117,"A sì fi ìmísí ránṣẹ́ sí (Ànábì) Mūsā pé: “Ju ọ̀pá rẹ sílẹ̀.” Nígbà náà, ó sì ń gbé ohun tí wọ́n ti pa nírọ́ kalẹ̀ mì kálókáló"
  7,118,"Nítorí náà, òdodo dé. Ohun tí wọ́n ń ṣe níṣẹ́ sì bàjẹ́"
  7,119,"Nítorí náà, A borí wọn níbẹ̀ yẹn. Wọ́n sì darí wálé ní ẹni yẹpẹrẹ"
  7,120,"Iṣẹ́ ìyanu (Ànábì Mūsā) mú àwọn òpìdán wólẹ̀, tí wọ́n forí kanlẹ̀ (fún Allāhu)"
  7,121,"Wọ́n sọ pé: \"A gbàgbọ́ nínú Olúwa gbogbo ẹ̀dá"
  7,122,Olúwa (Ànábì) Mūsā àti Hārūn
  7,123,"Fir‘aon wí pé: “Ẹ ti gbà Á gbọ́ ṣíwájú kí n̄g tó yọ̀ǹda fun yín! Dájúdájú èyí ni ète kan tí ẹ ti hun nínú ìlú nítorí kí ẹ lè kó àwọn ará ìlú jáde kúrò nínú rẹ̀. Nítorí náà, láìpẹ́ ẹ máa mọ̀"
  7,124,"Dájúdájú mo máa gé ọwọ́ yín àti ẹsẹ̀ yín ní ìpasípayọ. Lẹ́yìn náà, dájúdájú mo máa kan gbogbo yín mọ́gi.”"
  7,125,"Wọ́n sọ pé: \"Dájúdájú ọ̀dọ̀ Olúwa wa sì ni a máa fàbọ̀ sí"
  7,126,"Àti pé o ò tako kiní kan lára wa láti fìyà jẹ wá bí kò ṣe nítorí pé a gba àwọn àmì Olúwa wa gbọ́ nígbà tí ó dé bá wa. Olúwa wa, fún wa ní omi sùúrù mu. Kí O sì pa wá sípò mùsùlùmí"